@page "/"
@using JoinClass.Web.Components.Layout

<PageTitle>JoinClass - Tema Personalizado</PageTitle>

<h1>Tema JoinClass para MudBlazor</h1>

<p>Bem-vindo ao tema personalizado JoinClass baseado nas variáveis CSS dos seus arquivos HTML.</p>

<div class="d-flex gap-3 mb-3">
    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled" Color="Color.Primary">Botão Primário</MudButton>
    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled" Color="Color.Secondary">Botão Secundário</MudButton>
    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Outlined" Color="Color.Success">Botão de Sucesso</MudButton>
    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Warning">Botão de Aviso</MudButton>
</div>

<MudCard>
    <MudCardHeader>
        <CardHeaderContent>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Exemplo de Card</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">Este card demonstra o uso do tema JoinClass</MudText>
        </CardHeaderContent>
    </MudCardHeader>
    <MudCardContent>
        <MudText>
            O tema foi criado baseado nas variáveis CSS dos seus arquivos HTML:
        </MudText>
    </MudCardContent>
    <MudCardActions>
        <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Info">Saber Mais</MudButton>
    </MudCardActions>
</MudCard>

<MudGrid>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="6" md="3">
        <MudCard>
            <MudCardContent>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-center">
                    <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.School" Color="Color.Primary" Size="Size.Large" />
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="mt-2">Aulas</MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Secondary">Gerencie suas aulas</MudText>
                </div>
            </MudCardContent>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>

    <MudItem xs="12" sm="6" md="3">
        <MudCard>
            <MudCardContent>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-center">
                    <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.People" Color="Color.Success" Size="Size.Large" />
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="mt-2">Alunos</MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Secondary">Gerencie alunos</MudText>
                </div>
            </MudCardContent>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>

    <MudItem xs="12" sm="6" md="3">
        <MudCard>
            <MudCardContent>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-center">
                    <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.CalendarToday" Color="Color.Warning" Size="Size.Large" />
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="mt-2">Calendário</MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Secondary">Veja eventos</MudText>
                </div>
            </MudCardContent>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>

    <MudItem xs="12" sm="6" md="3">
        <MudCard>
            <MudCardContent>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-center">
                    <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Payment" Color="Color.Error" Size="Size.Large" />
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="mt-2">Faturamento</MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Secondary">Controle financeiro</MudText>
                </div>
            </MudCardContent>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>
</MudGrid>

<MudAlert Severity="Severity.Info" Class="mt-3">
    <strong>Dica:</strong> Este tema foi criado baseado nas variáveis CSS dos seus arquivos HTML originais e inclui
    suporte para tema claro e escuro, tipografia Inter/Roboto, sombras personalizadas e border-radius de 12px.
</MudAlert>

